With,the,Multimedia,Messaging,Service,MMS,users,can,send,messages,from,their,mobile,device,to,an,application,mobile,originate,or,an,application,can,send,messages,to,one,or,more,mobile,users,mobile,terminate,The,MMS,content,can,include,video,images,audio,and,synchronized,multimedia,integration,language,SMIL,formatting,as,well,as,plain,text,The,API,uses,REST,and,SOAP,protocols,Data,formats,include,JSON,and,XML